@{fg shine}@{b}Saga eXtended Mouse Daemon (XMouseD)@{ub}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}
Minimal, efficient mouse wheel daemon (7.4 KB) for Vampire/Apollo SAGA chipset.

XMouseD is a lightweight background daemon that monitors USB mouse wheel and button movements from the SAGA chipset hardware, then injects standard NewMouse-compatible scroll events into the Amiga input system. This allows any Amiga application to scroll using your mouse wheel without special drivers or modifications.@endnode

