@node "installation" "Installation"
@toc "saga-extended-mouse-xmouse"
@prev "quick-start-30-seconds"
@next "usage-configuration"
@{b}Installation@{ub}
   1. Download `XMouseD` from @{"Releases" system "OpenURL https://github.com/your-repo/releases"} : https://github.com/your-repo/releases

2. Copy to `C:` (or `SYS:C/`)

3. Add to `S:User-Startup`:

```

XMouseD

```

4. Restart or run `XMouseD` manually

Your mouse wheel now works in all applications. Press CTRL+C to stop, or just reboot.

@{b}Note@{ub}: Future versions will include an Installer script. For now, manual setup via User-Startup.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@endnode

