@node "adjusting-scroll-speed" "Adjusting Scroll Speed"
@toc "saga-extended-mouse-xmouse"
@prev "basic-commands"
@next "hot-config-update"
@{b}Adjusting Scroll Speed@{ub}
If scrolling is too slow or too fast, adjust polling interval without restarting:

@{code}
XMouseD 0x13         # Default Balanced (recommended)

XMouseD 0x21         # Slower/smoother (20ms)

XMouseD 0x31         # Even slower (40ms - better on slow CPU)

XMouseD 0x01         # Faster (5ms - may feel jittery)

@{plain}@endnode

@node "hot-config-update" "Hot Config Update"
@toc "saga-extended-mouse-xmouse"
@prev "adjusting-scroll-speed"
@next "command-arguments"
@{b}Hot Config Update@{ub}
If XMouse SAGA daemon is already running, launch with a new config byte to update settings instantly:

@{code}
XMouseD 0x13         # Start daemon or update config

XMouseD 0x21         # Update to 20ms (no restart needed!)

XMouseD 0x93         # Enable debug mode

XMouseD 0x13         # Disable debug mode

XMouseD 0x00         # Stop daemon

@{plain}@endnode

